	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi all!
<br />
<br />I'm looking to get some PCBs fabbed and was wondering if anyone were interested in helping me out.
<br />
<br />I'm looking to pretty much make a copy of a pre-existing PCB, but have no experience or knowledge in how to draw up a proper schematic that I could send for production.  If I were to provide the original PCB I wanted to essentially copy, would anyone be willing to draw up a schematic that I could send to a manufacturer?
<br />
<br />If anyone is interested, feel free to shoot me a PM.  I'd be very interested in paying for your help!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


