<br />
<br />It's basically a 4MB Genesis board with battery backed SRAM.  I could mail out the exact board I'm looking to basically reproduce to anyone interested in helping out.
<br />
<br />As far as schematic vs board layout, I apologize for my ignorance but I don't fully even understand the terminology.  Basically, I want something that I can send to a PCB manufacture and say "build this" and be all set.
<br />
<br />I'm very motivated with cash in hand, if someone wants to make $100+ for pretty much copying a preexisting layout, hit me up <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

