		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Search for a software that has Eagle format support. You can send that file and the PCB producer could make a 1:1 PCB with that design
<br />
<br />Try ExpressPCB. I usually use ExpressSCH for schematics, but I haven't tried ExpressPCB yet

		

		</td>
	</tr>
