	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />What you want is a set of gerbers (rs-274x aperture data) and excellon drill files.
<br />
<br />You will need to do some looking around with pcb shops and get some quotes. You can't lay out a pcb without knowing the specs that the fab shop will be able to use. capabilities of their equipment, blah blah

		

